<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_cfb0a8f1-ae42-467a-9ddd-b2d7e5316072" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>D3D16</sptc><title id="_1a58f3ed-c275-4dcf-9e7f-c456de0a6a1a">Thresholds</title><archive-num>2019: D2.15</archive-num><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2120_1.5.0.xml" variation="SA" variation-type="REPLACE">SA REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2117_1.3.0.xml" variation="NSW" variation-type="REPLACE">NSW REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_ba348030-296b-457b-8fb4-a79aaae1348c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_070905c9-b495-4cbe-9817-4f4ba258843f">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The threshold of a doorway must not incorporate a step or ramp at any point closer to the doorway than the width of the door leaf unless<xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:15:00" xt:id="6572ece0-117c-4e8a-8067-f46a723d5cfa"/> the doorway opens to an external space<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="6572ece0-117c-4e8a-8067-f46a723d5cfa"/><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Lee Liu" xt:dateTime="2025-01-14T08:38:00" xt:id="5dbc396f-5467-4670-8586-0b6c1ecbdb5f"/>;<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="5dbc396f-5467-4670-8586-0b6c1ecbdb5f"/><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:15:00" xt:id="9a1aefc1-c703-4e1c-b1f3-542e25db7e32"/> and<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="9a1aefc1-c703-4e1c-b1f3-542e25db7e32"/>—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_a9c9587b-d632-4117-b791-8a6a5cbb4f57"><xt:delText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:00" xt:id="87e0faca-11e1-4676-a506-a5c20c93c7b4"/>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1393_4.0.0.xml#_63b56568-e9c9-425f-8456-a332503c9520" id="_b3e265db-083c-426f-ac3a-b5206388e6cb" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">patient care areas</xref> in a Class 9a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1333_0.4.0.xml#_1f5fbee8-584a-4244-9286-ebf9d8ebb04a" id="_01a9791f-7809-4eb0-a24b-00ea6dddf786" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">health-care building</xref>, the door sill is not more than 25 mm above the finished floor level to which the doorway opens; or<xt:delText xt:action="end" xt:id="87e0faca-11e1-4676-a506-a5c20c93c7b4"/><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:00" xt:id="228fa52c-50dd-47e4-beea-65b238264c51"/>where the doorway serves an area <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_44473567-4db3-45a4-808d-0521be95634e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_fa1db741-0151-41ff-bbb8-533213da34bd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/26_0.10.0.xml#_0422da33-ebd2-4d7c-994c-31d8dad5aa0f" id="_02523fac-e6c8-4d27-ab69-c5b10b03f022" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-part">Part D4</xref>, it is provided with a threshold ramp or step ramp in accordance with AS 1428.1; or<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="228fa52c-50dd-47e4-beea-65b238264c51"/></li><li id="_af7918d9-2222-4c34-8a50-37b0ecb2bc08"><xt:delText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:32:00" xt:id="42aa1f7f-5a04-45d7-985c-81697e1f8376"/>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1437_4.0.0.xml#_071db02d-667d-447e-9f1e-8de8c46b9e0e" id="_f246438a-27ab-4125-b85d-98413579f9ab" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">resident use areas</xref> in a Class 9c building, a ramp is provided with a maximum gradient of 1:8 for a maximum height of 25 mm over the threshold; or<xt:delText xt:action="end" xt:id="42aa1f7f-5a04-45d7-985c-81697e1f8376"/><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:33:00" xt:id="2fcdeaf7-914c-459a-ae28-5e295d77e439"/>where (a) does not apply, the door sill is not located below, and is not more than 190 mm above, the finished surface of the ground, balcony, or the like to which the doorway opens.<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="2fcdeaf7-914c-459a-ae28-5e295d77e439"/></li><li id="_1fdc31b8-9e90-4467-b18e-6f8fc8235335" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:18" xt:type="delete"><xt:delText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:00" xt:id="c1c89b9a-faf6-428e-915e-8ead76731e10"/>in a building <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_b30ea17e-db70-4500-bd96-cd17340a322e" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:18" xt:type="delete">required</xref> to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_44c3efbd-e6c0-4558-9bf8-05bf64b36d79" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:18" xt:type="delete">accessible</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/26_0.10.0.xml#_0422da33-ebd2-4d7c-994c-31d8dad5aa0f" id="_bb6ebed8-f408-4468-af53-7383962b264b" scope="local" type="part" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:18" xt:type="delete">Part D4</xref>, the doorway—<xt:delText xt:action="end" xt:id="c1c89b9a-faf6-428e-915e-8ead76731e10"/><ol xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:18" xt:type="delete"><li xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:18" xt:type="delete"><xt:delText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:00" xt:id="81ded225-5d36-4788-a66f-f10032352a77"/>opens to a road or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1385_0.4.0.xml#_b4a20ca6-0197-4381-9e50-85c757fa574f" id="_9a52a320-0110-44c1-a10a-8d752f754c15" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:18" xt:type="delete">open space</xref>; and<xt:delText xt:action="end" xt:id="81ded225-5d36-4788-a66f-f10032352a77"/></li><li xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:18" xt:type="delete"><xt:delText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:00" xt:id="5e137e29-fb91-439a-8ab9-4d5e91f17bdf"/>is provided with a threshold ramp or step ramp in accordance with AS 1428.1; or<xt:delText xt:action="end" xt:id="5e137e29-fb91-439a-8ab9-4d5e91f17bdf"/></li></ol></li><li id="_4e14d5f5-b331-4899-847c-62705cad3aca" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:12" xt:type="delete"><xt:delText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:00" xt:id="324bcfd3-c879-40cb-9764-a547f7bdcdd6"/>in other cases—<xt:delText xt:action="end" xt:id="324bcfd3-c879-40cb-9764-a547f7bdcdd6"/><ol xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:12" xt:type="delete"><li xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:12" xt:type="delete"><xt:delText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:00" xt:id="5fa9b600-65a8-4a25-a734-ba71c81114c5"/>the doorway opens to a road or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1385_0.4.0.xml#_b4a20ca6-0197-4381-9e50-85c757fa574f" id="_ab627db2-5a9e-4bc5-8888-b0c82e640c00" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:12" xt:type="delete">open space</xref>, external stair landing or external balcony; and<xt:delText xt:action="end" xt:id="5fa9b600-65a8-4a25-a734-ba71c81114c5"/></li><li xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:12" xt:type="delete"><xt:delText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T10:16:00" xt:id="c9fccab8-8c3c-4519-8173-fc7086e9028e"/>the door sill is not more than 190 mm above the finished surface of the ground, balcony, or the like, to which the doorway opens.<xt:delText xt:action="end" xt:id="c9fccab8-8c3c-4519-8173-fc7086e9028e"/></li></ol></li></ol></subclause><callout id="_60f3ebe7-27fe-495e-80d4-e12b6a8f81dd" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:25:35" xt:type="insert"><callout-type ncc-info-type="exemption" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:25:36" xt:type="insert"/><p xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:25:56" xt:type="insert"><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:25:00" xt:id="a9b28ffc-4f2d-452f-a573-c4cc981da6d2"/>D3D16 does not apply to a plant room, machinery room, or the like.<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="a9b28ffc-4f2d-452f-a573-c4cc981da6d2"/></p></callout><callout id="_fcffcac8-c1f0-472f-a1a4-2da19d30cbdc" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:26:21" xt:type="insert"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:26:21" xt:type="insert"/><title id="_95c965a0-d586-4021-b28a-efe17662fa9c" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:26:37" xt:type="insert"><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:26:00" xt:id="d78f1521-6d4b-49dc-9d62-528bf17a81ce"/>Read in conjunction with D4D3<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="d78f1521-6d4b-49dc-9d62-528bf17a81ce"/></title><p xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:26:58" xt:type="insert"><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:27:00" xt:id="db1382bd-069e-4671-a152-b2336fdd6a44"/>D3D16(a) is to be read in conjunction with D4D3, which requires some external doorways to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_993031ad-6dfc-4262-8b12-52b7f6ca9259" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref>. In order to comply with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2035_1.3.0.xml#_95b0e5ea-8488-4ba8-a40c-e60fa1eeed8e" id="_15d4b154-f72c-40b7-ad68-21193839310a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">D4D3</xref>, the thresholds of these doorways cannot incorporate a ramp within the width of the door leaf.<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="db1382bd-069e-4671-a152-b2336fdd6a44"/></p></callout><callout id="_1efded2c-8b8f-41f4-bbae-b31e2ed2221b" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:33:28" xt:type="insert"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:33:28" xt:type="insert"/><title id="_5d6f4772-ba01-46c8-8f06-57c0fd5769cd" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:33:33" xt:type="insert"><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:33:00" xt:id="ae565a1f-bef6-4c61-8acc-967f019437b7"/>Bunds<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="ae565a1f-bef6-4c61-8acc-967f019437b7"/></title><p xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:33:56" xt:type="insert"><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-18T08:47:00" xt:id="6beff253-a7ba-462a-8386-c1eb0dc62039"/>D3D16 does not prevent the addition of a bund within the width of the door leaf from the doorway. However, this is to be considered in conjunction with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2034_1.12.0.xml#_396cb0f6-6ff5-49da-9c51-d4ba94a22e79" id="_e53b2f2c-5dc1-48f6-8a73-d6b1b219ee6d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">D4D2</xref> that requires certain areas to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_12a184b6-31ad-4697-b921-9578848ef2d2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> which may prevent the incorporation of a bund.<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="6beff253-a7ba-462a-8386-c1eb0dc62039"/></p></callout></clause>